ars in hospitality industry. His can do attitude is never defeating and applauded across stakeholders and his team. He is a rare talent. Wish him luck.", "recommendationsReceived/7/name": "Gaurav Sinha", "recommendationsReceived/7/subtitle": "Hotel Manager at JW Marriott Bangaluru", "recommendationsReceived/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gaurav-sinha-50363a18/", "recommendationsReceived/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAOnQVMBorGyNGkpyEEC0IUNdux7xExB3DY", "recommendationsReceived/8/context": "Rajani worked with Shrey  on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/8/date": "October 5, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/8/description": "Shrey has been an integral part of the pre- opening team for prestigious Pullman- Novotel Aerocity complex. His skills combined with his enthusiasm were highly noted. He is a fast learner and full of ideas. A self motivated and great leader for his peers. Wish him luck for all his future endeavors.", "recommendationsReceived/8/name": "Rajani Sushil", "recommendationsReceived/8/subtitle": "Head of Sales at Essai", "recommendationsReceived/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rajani-sushil-73ba695/", "recommendationsReceived/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAEL7t8ByqICX_wDWPHTJSjlloBMi7JMBvU", "recommendationsReceived/9/context": "Prasenjit reported directly to Shrey ", "recommendationsReceived/9/date": "September 26, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/9/description": "An Amazing leader with absolutely fantastic skills and great team handling capabilities ... A dear friend at and outside work.. Overall an amazing resource for any organisation.. ", "recommendationsReceived/9/name": "Prasenjit Chakraborty", "recommendationsReceived/9/subtitle": "Sales and Marketing", "recommendationsReceived/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/prasenjit-chakraborty-7705a4110/", "recommendationsReceived/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABvaBUQBN6mdeyoylUc4GQhVDhqDwo1kiso", "recommendationsReceived/10/context": "Rajat worked with Shrey  but on different teams"