ic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E03AQFm0n156Wj7Dw/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1597224081618?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=HQvcr5h6suNLmg-L45E-RTnp7vJCbt2IWk7ET5jAHwo", "profilePicHighQuality": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E03AQFm0n156Wj7Dw/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1597224081618?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=HQvcr5h6suNLmg-L45E-RTnp7vJCbt2IWk7ET5jAHwo", "publicIdentifier": "olivier-le-guyader-45baab9", "recommendations/0/context": "Olivier managed Élodie directly", "recommendations/0/date": "September 11, 2024", "recommendations/0/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Élodie during my tenure as General Manager at 110 de Taillevent restaurant in Paris, and I can confidently say that she was an invaluable asset to our team. From day one, Élodie demonstrated exceptional organizational skills, a keen eye for detail, and an unwavering commitment to excellence.\n\nHer ability to manage multiple tasks while maintaining a positive attitude and professionalism was truly impressive. Élodie took initiative in streamlining operations, which significantly improved our workflow and efficiency. She was not only efficient in her role but also a fantastic team player, always willing to lend a helping hand and support her colleagues.\n\nWhat stood out the most was Élodie's extraordinary communication skills. She fostered strong relationships with both staff and guests, ensuring that every interaction was memorable and positive. Her dedication to customer service was evident in everything she did, which contributed greatly to our restaurant’s success.\n\nI wholeheartedly recommend Élodie for any future endeavors. Her passion, dedication, and talent will undoubtedly make her a valuable asset wherever she goes.\n\n", "recommendations/0/name": "Élodie Batut", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Hospitality Professional l Senior Restaurant Manager l Operations, Team Leadership & Guest Experience", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/élodie-batut-16646453/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAtHod4BKR9ITNsBj65qRRF5wN3O1pQNBUM", "recommendations/1/context": "Olivier managed Valentin directly", "recommendations/1/date": "May 3, 2023", "recommendations/1/description": "Valentin and I worked together at Epure where I was his Director, I thoroughly enjoyed my time working with him and he was a truly valuable asset to the team.\nHe was honest, loyal and incredibly hard - working.\nHe was an impressive problem solver and always addressed issues with strategy and confidence.\nValentin was inspired by challenges and never intimidated by them.\nHis knowledge of customer service and expertise was a huge advantage to the entire team, he also put his skill set to work in order to increase our sales revenue. \nIf I got the opportunity I hire him again anytime!", "recommendations/1/name": "Valentin GIRARD", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Luxury Guest Experience & Turnaround Operations Manager | International Operations, Partner Coordination & Training & Knowledge Sharing", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/valentin-girard-966a33143/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACLbtJ4BE6c_zcGLQ3tkK0FxGIqcZlifT7A", "recommendations/2/context": "Olivier worked with Sheldon on the same team", "recommendations/2/date": "February 27, 2020", "recommendations/2/description": "\nI had the great opportunity to work with Sheldon during the all project of La Petite Maison in Hong Kong.\nSheldon has done a tremendous job starting from scratch on this project and delivering an outstanding job by building the team, all procurement aspect, managing the quality and consistency by delivering the brand standard since pre- opening to daily operation.\nI will be happy to work again with Sheldon in the future!\n", "recommendations/2/name": "Sheldon Fonseca", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Park Hyatt Phu Quoc", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sheldon-fonseca-368722/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAbRYABQBIA8gidT3QrLZQktgE9AnGkVnU", "recommendations/3/context": "Olivier managed guillaume directly", "recommendations/3/date": "October 9, 2018", "recommendations/3/description": "I had the pleasure to work with Guillaume when I arrived in Hong Kong and he was directly reporting to me.\nGuillaume always shown a strong ownership and he is reliable, honest and truly committed to his work at all time.\nA role model to many F&B professional as always looking to do the extra mile to make the overall business successful in all aspects.\nIf I have the opportunity to work again with Guillaume I won’t hesitate a second.\nGuillaume deliver and make things happening!\nHe was an asset to the company.\nI highly recommend him!", "recommendations/3/name": "guillaume P.", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Cluster General Manager - Lifestyle Hotels at Millennium Hotels & Resorts", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/guillaume-places/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAARPJUsBCDkfaCcT8RLJk-M0L6hTQ8ECmrM", "recommendations/4/context": "Olivier worked with Sandrine on the same team", "recommendations/4/date": "July 20, 2017", "recommendations/4/description": "J'ai eu l'immense plaisir de travailler avec Sandrine wind j'étais en poste pour la maison Taillevent.\nSandrine à démontrer à chaque moment un grand professionnalisme avec une grande adaptabilité aux challenges qu'elle devait gérer.\nSo l'occasion se présente je serai ravi de collaborer de nouveau avec Sandrine car ce fut une employée exemplaire dans le milieu administrative de la restauration de luxe.\n ", "recommendations/4/name": "Sandrine Bonin 💎 Coach d'Identité", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Executive COACH certifié - Outplacement - Transition professionnelle - Conduite du changement - Leadership au féminin", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandrinebonin/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAwsyaoBcaurrKQhOw0GH-b15Jy0QhC92t0", "recommendations/5/context": "Olivier worked with Brice on the same team", "recommendations/5/date": "February 23, 2017", "recommendations/5/description": "Brice was an outstanding employee and extremely knowledgeable for the wines industry.\nHe always adapt himself to business needs and has a great customer service ability.\nI will be happy to recommend Brice under any circonstances.", "recommendations/5/name": "Brice Mancelet", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "Spécialiste commercialisation en vin", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/brice-mancelet-4a856b87/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABJqHwABiu_0TKjtYjTBkRVla0NKN4PV1YY", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "guillaume reported directly to Olivier", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "October 9, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "I had the pleasure to work with Olivier when we were both in Epure Hong Kong.\nOlivier is what i consider the closest to my mentor, both through his professional ethics and his friendly approach to team building and management.\nIt would be my great pleasure to work again together somedays.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "guillaume P.", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Cluster General Manager - Lifestyle Hotels at Millennium Hotels & Resorts", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/guillaume-places/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAARPJUsBCDkfaCcT8RLJk-M0L6hTQ8ECmrM", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Olivier was Aurore's client", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "September 19, 2017", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I have been working with Olivier for several years, when he was the director of \"Taillevent - les 110\".\nHe 's been the one who shaped this new pionner concept, he had a large vision of it. This restaurant is a great success and everybody misses Olivier's professionalism, joy and continuous good humour.\n\nI highly recommend Olivier for employment. He is a quick learner, energetic, and hardworking\nand would make a great asset to any organization. \n\n", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Aurore Monot-Devillard", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Château de Chamirey - Domaine des Perdrix", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/aurore-monot-devillard-571a75/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAoU-UBT7y9SQ6g0JdI2DRaI8LmmuZlAjQ", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Mickaël was Olivier's client", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "August 18, 2017", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "in the frame of a professional seminar with many nationalities, I asked Olivier Le Guyader to organize a tasting meeting in Paris a few years ago. Unbelievable in the preparation phase, he knew how to give us the ideas to make this moment different. Above all, he was able to accompany us and meet the expectations of our guests whether they are novices or experts. Perfect on all details, he has this little French Touch that is so difficult to explain. A lot of talent !", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Mickaël DAVILA", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Entreprise Architecte | IA, Compliance, & Security Architecture | Transition Manager | Leading IT Certifications", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mickaeldavila/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAajRsBqXYFrgmBlIU5pD6ghtAYwnzbpcs", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Olivier was senior to Brice but didn't manage Brice directly", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "February 23, 2017", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "I had known Olivier over a 4 years period and was always truly impress by his outstanding performance in all aspect of his duties.\nFrom the transition of a fine gourmet restaurant in too the most sought after Food and Wine pairing establishment in Paris.\nHis management’s skill in planning, costing  hiring, training and motivating staff that are front or back office are second to none.\nHis attention to details coupled with a remarkable personality ensures that service never wavered and that guest feels first class.\n", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Brice Mancelet", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Spécialiste commercialisation en vin", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/brice-mancelet-4a856b87/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABJqHwABiu_0TKjtYjTBkRVla0NKN4PV1YY", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Brenda was Olivier's client", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "January 19, 2017", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "Emprendedor, muy trabajador y responsable. Profesional y muy comprometido en cada proyecto que emprende. Habilidades directivas y trabajo en equipo", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Brenda Máñez", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "--", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/brenda-máñez-17116710a/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABtugiUBdZazCc4HsfIqU9pCL1TDSj1DQhU", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Bruno was Olivier's client", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "September 22, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "Aussi bien dans la version \"Angle du Faubourg\" qu'aujourd'hui, sous l'égide \"110 Taillevant\", Olivier est un directeur très dynamique et efficace : discret et sachant s'adapter à la variété de sa clientèle, manageant ses équipes avec diligence et soutien, Olivier possède en plus une grande acuité et intelligence des situations, qui font que l'on retourne toujours avec autant de plaisir dans son restaurant !", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Bruno ERHARD", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "Directeur des affaires publiques et de la communication chez Boehringer Ingelheim France", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bruno-erhard/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAWP4z0BKm7IxIzZciLyUypGPgJ7J0J0aHQ", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Sandrine worked with Olivier but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "September 18, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "J'ai eu beaucoup de plaisir à travailler en synergie avec Olivier, qui est un Manager très ouvert, toujours disponible pour son équipe et avec un grand sens du service client.\n \nIl représente l'image de marque du Groupe Taillevent, de par son charisme, ses qualités d'écoute et son expertise.\n\nJe lui souhaite une belle réussite professionnelle.\n\nSandrine Bonin", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Sandrine Bonin 💎 Coach d'Identité", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "Executive COACH certifié - Outplacement - Transition professionnelle - Conduite du changement - Leadership au féminin", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandrinebonin/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAwsyaoBcaurrKQhOw0GH-b15Jy0QhC92t0", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Nicolas worked with Olivier but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "September 18, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/7/description": "Olivier est un excellent manager d'équipes et un grand professionnel de la restauration.\nAussi, il sait évoluer au sein d'un Groupe multi-activités en comprenant les enjeux et les contraintes.\nJe le recommande fortement pour différentes fonctions d'encadrement dans le secteur hôtellerie-restauration.", "recommendationsReceived/7/name": "Nicolas Quintin", "recommendationsReceived/7/subtitle": "Directeur Administratif et Financier Carter-Cash Mobivia Group", "recommendationsReceived/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicolas-quintin-b1b2241b/", "recommendationsReceived/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQgS0cBg96mBPTy25JdSds1Dq2Pj7lHa-k", "recommendationsReceived/8/context": "Christophe worked with Olivier but th